  "text": "Non-canonical palm connectivity has also been described in the RdRP encoded by Grapevine virus Q (GVQ) [CITATION_1] , an alpha-like plant tymovirus. However, bioinformatics analyses suggest that whereas the permuted RdRPs from birna-and permutotetraviruses share a monophyletic origin that of GVQ evolved independently [CITATION_2] .",
